&lt;Sale Tilney Plc> said it has purchased80 pct of the ordinary share capital of &lt;B and R InternationalInc.>, a U.S. Insurance broker, for 5.6 mln dlrs.    Sale is paying 3.6 mln dlrs in cash on completion, with thebalance plus interest to be paid in equal instalments over thenext six years.    B and R posted pretax profit of 855,000 dlrs in the year toDec 31, 1986 when it had net tangible assets of 563,000 dlrs. REUTER&#3;